{"id":177,"date":"2017-02-11T10:18:14","date_gmt":"2017-02-11T10:18:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=177"},"modified":"2019-03-24T14:40:20","modified_gmt":"2019-03-24T14:40:20","slug":"redirect-contact-to-another-page-after-login","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/redirect-contact-to-another-page-after-login\/","title":{"rendered":"Redirect contact to another page after login"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>If you need to redirect contact after login to some custom URL or some other URL inside the CRM you can do it with action hook.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a file with name <a href=\"https:\/\/www.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/my_functions_helper.zip\"><strong>my_functions_helper.php<\/strong><\/a> in&nbsp;application\/helpers\/ and add the following code:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Version 2.3.0 or above<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;?php\n\n\/\/ After contact login from the login form\nhooks()->add_action('after_contact_login','redirect_to_projects');\n\/\/ After client registered and logged in automatically\nhooks()->add_action('after_client_register_logged_in','redirect_to_projects');\n\nfunction redirect_to_projects(){\nredirect(site_url('clients\/projects'));\n}<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Prior to version 2.3.0<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;?php\n\n\/\/ After contact login from the login form\nadd_action('after_contact_login','redirect_to_projects');\n\/\/ After client registered and logged in automatically\nadd_action('after_client_register_logged_in','redirect_to_projects');\n\nfunction redirect_to_projects(){\nredirect(site_url('clients\/projects'));\n}<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an example where the contact will be redirected to the projects view inside the CRM, however, you can adjust the URL to fit for your requirements.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":